title: DSCI Recruitment 2025 - Walk-in-Interview for 39 Senior Resident Posts
description: Delhi State Cancer Institute (DSCI) has declared the latest job notification for 2025. To fill up the vacancies for 39 Senior Resident Posts. Those candidates who have qualified in the MBBS, MD/ MS, DNB, and Post-Graduation can grab this chance and apply for the DSCI Recruitment 2025 . Here, we include the age limit, selection process, salary structure, education details, application fee, and how to apply for these posts.
